ROSEN--Louis, 81, on April 30, 2013 after battling a particularly aggressive cancer for only six months. He leaves his broken-hearted wife of almost 57 years, Barbara, and adoring children, Allison and Jonathan. Words cannot begin to express how terribly he will be missed. Funeral service Thursday, May 2, 2013, 11:30am at Frank E. Campbell The Funeral Chapel, Madison Avenue at 81 Street, NYC.